      <memberdef kind="define" id="group__devicetree-ranges-prop_1ga4c71a8adcfe6c53b480775510c92a632" prot="public" static="no">
        <name>DT_FOREACH_RANGE</name>
        <param><defname>node_id</defname></param>
        <param><defname>fn</defname></param>
        <initializer>	DT_CAT(node_id, _FOREACH_RANGE)(fn)</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Invokes <computeroutput>fn</computeroutput> for each entry of <computeroutput>node_id</computeroutput> ranges property. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The macro <computeroutput>fn</computeroutput> must take two parameters, <computeroutput>node_id</computeroutput> which will be the node identifier of the node with the ranges property and <computeroutput>idx</computeroutput> the index of the ranges block.</para>
<para>Example devicetree fragment:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".dts"><codeline><highlight class="normal">n:<sp/>node@0<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>reg<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;0<sp/>0<sp/>1&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>ranges<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;0x0<sp/>0x0<sp/>0x0<sp/>0x3eff0000<sp/>0x10000&gt;,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;0x0<sp/>0x10000000<sp/>0x0<sp/>0x10000000<sp/>0x2eff0000&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Example usage:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".c"><codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#define<sp/>RANGE_LENGTH(node_id,<sp/>idx)<sp/>DT_RANGES_LENGTH_BY_IDX(node_id,<sp/>idx),</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">const</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/><ref refid="stdint_8h_1a2095b9bffea4b2656950c6c0419edbf1" kindref="member">uint64_t</ref><sp/>*ranges_length[]<sp/>=<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><ref refid="group__devicetree-ranges-prop_1ga4c71a8adcfe6c53b480775510c92a632" kindref="member">DT_FOREACH_RANGE</ref>(<ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-id_1gab7d23294a6bf7fd44a98b48ec47d8a79" kindref="member">DT_NODELABEL</ref>(n),<sp/>RANGE_LENGTH)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
